Colors:
    Primary: #000000 (black)
    Secondary: #E0AA3E (0xFFE0AA3E)
These colors complement each other. App has no white for widgets, just backgrounds

Header texts are black with background as secondary. No border radius, just sharp edges and corners.
Also, no padding between edges and text.

Slider:
    track color - secondary
    thumb color - primary

SCREENS
1. Main (L&L)
- Debt, To Earn (action goes to financials)
- L&L activity: list of their transactions
- Keypad
- Payment methods
2. Financials
Money owed or expected to earn
Graphs
Calculations

3. Activity
View requests
Accept bob requests (place bids)
View status of loan requests and verify bob requests initiated by user

4. Profile


Font ideas
- familjenGrotesk
- urbanist
- davidLibre
- spaceGrotesk
- manrope
- lexend


Credit score info:
i. Telephone number
ii. Name
iii. ID Number
iv. Email address
v. Call logs, SMS logs
vi. Information from credit reference bureaus
vii. Phone IMEI

*** Check Credit Reference Bureau online


Money
3% commission (lender pays)
Borrower repays loans starting at 3% continuously compounded





